reasons.another: Upayogakarta ne bina iss ek se disconnect kiye sidhe dusre server se connect kar liya.
reasons.banned: Upayogkarta ko staff ke sadasya ne diye gaye kaaran ke saath ban kiya.
reasons.config: Jodte samay server ki vinyas load nahi ho pa rahi thi jis wajah se upayogakarta ko aswikar kar diya gaya.
reasons.crash: Upayogkarta ka khel diye gaye error sandesh ke saath band ho gaya.
reasons.disconnected: Upayogkarta ne 'disconnect' likhkar F8 console mein ya usi prakaar server se vichchhed kiya.
reasons.doors: Server ne client ke sath darwaze ko synchronize karne ki koshish ki lekin asafal raha, isliye yah truti se ubhar nahi pa raha tha aur upayogakarta ko server se nikal diya gaya.
reasons.editor: Khiladi ne unka Rockstar Editor khola jo swatah hi aapko vartaman server se bahar kar deta hai.
reasons.exited: Upayogkarta ne khel se 'quit' likhkar F8 console mein ya ALT aur F4 dabakar ya usi prakaar chhoda.
reasons.global: Pranali ne pata lagaya ki upayogakarta shayad kuch galat kar raha tha aur use ek vishwa OP-FW pratispardha ki saja di.
reasons.job: Upayogakarta ka job prathmikta samapt ho gayi. Iska matlab hai ki job prathmikta ke liye lambi katari mein upayogakarta bahut samay tak raha is karan se pranali ne unhe katari se bahar kar diya.
reasons.kicked: Upayogakarta ko kisi karan se staff sadasya dwara bahar nikala gaya.
reasons.overflow: Cheaters dwara aapke server par events ki spamming se bachne ke liye FiveM dwara suraksha upay.
reasons.reloading_game: Upayogakarta ne F8 console ya uske saman kisi anya madhyam se 'localGame' command ka upayog karke ek single-player khel load kiya.
reasons.restart: Upayogkarta ko server ne kick kiya kyunki server restart ho raha tha.
reasons.timeout: Upayogkarta ka server se sambandh kaat gaya. Aam taur par yeh tab hota hai jab internet connectivity mein gap aa jata hai.
reasons.unknown: Vistarit varnan uplabdh nahi hai. Aap vikasak se adhik madad ke liye puch sakte hain.
